|----------|-----------|--------|
| H₁ ∈ so(7) | H₁ + H₁ᵀ = 0 | native_decide |
| H₂ ∈ so(7) | H₂ + H₂ᵀ = 0 | native_decide |
| H₁ ∈ g₂ | L_{H₁}(φ₀) = 0 | native_decide |
| H₂ ∈ g₂ | L_{H₂}(φ₀) = 0 | native_decide |
